		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You can drag either of the effects either off this item or from the Enchantments compendium. This will add the relevant property and adjust the value of the item.</em></p><p><em>Weapon (Any Simple or Martial)</em></p><p>This weapon is &amp;reference[adamantine].</p><p>Adamantine is a magical material harder and harder to break than any nonmagical metal. It can cut materials like steel and stone without a scratch.</p><ul><li><p>Most golems are resistant or immune to non-adamantine weapons. Magic weapons can damage these creatures, but not as effectively as adamantine weapons.​</p></li></ul>",
